        "name": "Stalwart Chant",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You know story after story of unyielding, valiant dwarven heroes whose minds were bulwarks against fear and confusion. You can use Stalwart Song when attempting a saving throw against any mental effect, and if you fail the saving throw, you gain resistance to mental damage against any resulting effect equal to half your level.",
